  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study wishes to compare patient satisfaction and cosmesis of two different closure
      methods of laparoscopic ports. One method uses tissue adhesive (Dermabond) with a deep
      sub-cutaneous stitch and a Band-Aid dressing. The comparison method uses a 3.o undyed vicryl
      transcutaneous stitch, with a Bacitracin and Tegaderm dressing.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
